A primary way of doing this is by decreasing the purchasing

4
00:00:11.152 --> 00:00:13.341
cost of materials.

5
00:00:13.341 --> 00:00:17.340
Prime Vendors, or PV, employ strategies to quickly deliver

6
00:00:17.340 --> 00:00:21.364
expensive products and avoid holding costly inventories

7
00:00:21.364 --> 00:00:24.516
in stores any longer than necessary.

8
00:00:24.516 --> 00:00:28.195
For example, Cardinal provides gowns to hospitals across

9
00:00:28.195 --> 00:00:31.624
the country, as a result of the volume and to the bulk

10
