otherwise skids of gowns will sit in the PV warehouses

12
00:00:39.247 --> 00:00:42.057
and take up valuable real estate that could be used

13
00:00:42.057 --> 00:00:44.794
to house other items, thus creating higher

14
00:00:44.794 --> 00:00:46.794
cost to the PV to store.

15
00:00:47.896 --> 00:00:50.359
In order for supply chains to work effectively

16
00:00:50.359 --> 00:00:53.748
and efficiently, logistics staff need to decrease

17
00:00:53.748 --> 00:00:56.815
the total cost to manage the supply chain.

18
00:00:56.815 --> 00:01:00.206
